column4: Our Software Testing course provides comprehensive training in the fundamental concepts and practices of software testing. Covering both manual and automated testing techniques participants will learn to design test cases execute tests and report defects effectively. Through hands-on exercises and real-world scenarios students will gain proficiency in industry-standard tools and methodologies equipping them with the skills necessary to ensure the quality and reliability of software systems. This course is ideal for beginners and professionals looking to enhance their expertise in software testing.
